{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MZLyLW9jMtqSVucQGFq9sz","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Story 17.1: Worktree Manager\n2\t\n3\tStatus: ready-for-dev\n4\t\n5\t## Story\n6\t\n7\tAs a developer,\n8\tI want a worktree manager that handles git worktree create/merge/cleanup,\n9\tso that parallel epics run in isolated working directories.\n10\t\n11\t## Acceptance Criteria\n12\t\n13\t1. **Given** `src/lib/worktree-manager.ts` exists, **when** `createWorktree(epicId, slug)` is called, **then** it creates a git branch named `codeharness/epic-{epicId}-{slug}` from the current HEAD of the main branch. <!-- verification: test-provable -->\n14\t\n15\t2. **Given** `createWorktree(epicId, slug)` is called, **when** the branch is created, **then** it creates a git worktree at `/tmp/codeharness-wt-epic-{epicId}` pointing to the new branch and returns the absolute worktree path. <!-- verification: test-provable -->"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01MhSojYxQi6QD3G7L9MYQcx","session_id":"187035da-d60e-40cf-8aef-09e6134be246","uuid":"7fd75b16-0a41-4447-913a-00c85fd92a8d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:22:57.088Z"}
