\n- 4768 tests pass, coverage 96.6%.\n\nToken Report: 18 tool calls (Bash: 8, Read: 4, Grep: 9, Write: 2, Glob: 1). 3 unique files, 4 reads. Lint and coverage each run twice — could combine.\n\n---\n\n### 16-6-story-flow-execution — create-story (2026-04-03T18:55)\n\n- Workflow template file (`workflow.md`) did not exist — adapted to follow `instructions.xml` directives.\n- Skipped web research and validation checklist interactive loop (autonomous mode).\n- Risk: Circuit breaker halts during loop means telemetry null tasks won't execute — documented as expected.\n- Risk: grep for `workflow.flow` consumers beyond engine could reveal unexpected references.\n- Observation: simplest story in epic 16 — essentially a one-line property rename plus tests.\n- All 6 ACs tagged `test-provable`.\n\nToken Report: 16 tool calls (Bash: 3, Read: 6, Grep: 6, Write: 1, Glob: 5, Skill: 1). 8 unique files, 8 total reads. No redundancy.\n\n### 16-6-story-flow-execution — dev-story (2026-04-03T18:58)\n\nNone. Clean implementation — 2-line engine change, 11 new tests, 4779 tests pass, 0 failures.\n\nToken Report: 20 tool calls (Bash: 4, Read: 8, Edit: 5, Grep: 4, Glob: 3, Write: 1, Skill: 1). 9 unique files, 9 total reads. No redundancy.\n\n### 16-6-story-flow-execution — code-review (2026-04-03T19:02)\n\n- HIGH: Verdict JSON delivered via `subagentResult` instead of `text` events in 3 tests. Engine ignores `subagentResult`; `parseVerdict` received wrong input. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: AC #2 \"telemetry after loop\" test had no loop; tested sequential ordering only. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: AC #3 assertions trivially true (`> 1`, `toBeDefined()`); did not verify actual iteration count. Fixed.\n- LOW (not fixed): `defaultExecution` constant duplicates `EXECUTION_DEFAULTS` from `hierarchical-flow.ts`.\n- LOW (not fixed): `setupDefaultMocks()` default `text: 'Done'` causes `parseVerdict('Done')` to throw in any test that doesn't override.\n- Coverage: 96.63% overall, all 176 files above 80% floor.\n- 4780